{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/debut-theme-sticky-navigation-bar-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":480,"date":"2020-12-15T08:20:00","date_gmt":"2020-12-15T08:20:00","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=480"},"modified":"2021-02-24T08:28:07","modified_gmt":"2021-02-24T08:28:07","slug":"debut-theme-sticky-navigation-bar-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/debut-theme-sticky-navigation-bar-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Debut Theme: sticky navigation bar tutorial"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p>Regardless of your business strategy one thing every theme should give you is: freedom. Freedom to A/B test whatever works or what does not work for you. <br /><br />Debut theme, while being an amazing theme, lacks a few essential features, like a sticky navigation bar. In this tutorial I&#8217;ll teach you how to install it.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Downloading the files</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>There are two options:<br />Download the <strong>free version</strong> clicking <a href=\"https://gumroad.com/l/debut-sticky-nav-free\">here</a> (<a href=\"https://debut-theme-slider-free.myshopify.com/products/blue-silk-tuxedo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>) &#8211; <strong>password</strong> is: 123<br />Download the <strong>pro version</strong> clicking <a href=\"https://ezfy.e-junkie.com/product/1689723\">here</a>. (<a href=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/products/blue-silk-tuxedo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>) <br /><br />The differences between the two are (<strong>options below can be turned on/off at the customize page)</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\">\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Features</th>\r\n<th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Pro</th>\r\n<th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Free</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sticky navbar on desktop</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sticky navbar on mobile</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sticky navbar on homepage only</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Navbar font size<br />(unique values for desktop/mobile)</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sticky announcement bar on desktop</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sticky announcement bar on mobile</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Sticky announcement bar <br />on homepage only</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Announcement bar font size<br />(unique values for desktop/mobile)</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Add subtle shadow below navbar</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fix: when clicking on &#8220;search&#8221;<br />page jumps to top</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fix: when opening the menu<br />page jumps to top</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fix: <br />Search input re-coded from scratch<br />to work with both sticky navbar <br />and the announcement bar</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Frequent updates</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fixes</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Constantly maintained</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">New features based on user feedback</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td>\r\n<td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Updating the header file (only for the free version)</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol id=\"block-dbf1fa37-09f6-4cb3-ad8d-83d260fc44e4\">\r\n<li>In your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store</strong> &gt; <strong>Themes </strong>&gt; <strong>Actions </strong>&gt; <strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Open the <strong>header.txt </strong>file that you downloaded and copy all the code in there.</li>\r\n<li>Now go back to your Shopify admin, find the <strong>header.liquid</strong> file in your theme.</li>\r\n<li>Delete everything in there and paste the code that you copied.</li>\r\n<li>Save. Make sure the first line says &#8220;Sticky Debut Header&#8221; like this:<br /><br /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"947\" height=\"709\" class=\"wp-image-188\" style=\"width: 1000px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/firstfile.jpg\" alt=\"Liquid code for Shopify\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/firstfile.jpg 947w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/firstfile-600x449.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/firstfile-768x575.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 947px) 100vw, 947px\" /></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Updating the Javascript file</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol id=\"block-c160b6c8-9f7f-4480-bb8d-a630157f9a7d\">\r\n<li>In your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store</strong> &gt; <strong>Themes </strong>&gt; <strong>Actions </strong>&gt; <strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Open the <strong>javascript.txt </strong>file that you downloaded and copy all the code in there.</li>\r\n<li>In your Shopify theme, find the file <strong>theme.js</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Scroll all the way down and, at the very bottom of the file, paste the code.</li>\r\n<li>Click on &#8220;save&#8221;.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Bonus for PRO users: fixing the page jumping bug</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#8217;re on mobile and click on &#8220;search&#8221; or the button to expand the menu you may notice that the page will jump up. There is a very easy simple way to fix this:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol id=\"block-f09ca9ff-30e0-46e2-a78c-7e73b2727e8f\">\r\n<li>In your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store</strong> &gt; <strong>Themes </strong>&gt; <strong>Actions </strong>&gt; <strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Find the file <strong>theme.js</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Press CTRL +F (or command + F on Mac) and search for <strong>(0, 0) </strong></li>\r\n<li>Delete this line. Here is how it looks like before and after:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"879\" height=\"661\" class=\"wp-image-189\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-4.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-4.png 879w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-4-600x451.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-4-768x578.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 879px) 100vw, 879px\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"816\" height=\"596\" class=\"wp-image-190\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-5.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-5.png 816w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-5-600x438.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-5-768x561.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br />Now you&#8217;re ready to use your Sticky navigation bar! Happy sales!</p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Add a sticky navigation bar to your theme in under one minute for free and effortlessly. </p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":345,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[6,3,7,12],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/debut-sticky-pro-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/debut-sticky-pro-100x100.png","post_count":0,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["code","debut","devtips","product"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/480"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=480"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/480/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":488,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/480/revisions/488"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/345"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=480"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=480"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=480"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1739988571","1995349551"]}